{"tid":1329460,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"另類文宣  #向香港年輕人致敬","createTime":"2019-07-18T08:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T01:48:29.000Z","uid":1110,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc20e437bc9b6035e4947d161bc052911874978a","tid":1329460,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"反送中運動已經持續一個月有多，文宣戰已經係重中之重。我地連登仔都要發揮下我地我地小宇宙  好好俾d創意打下呢場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個諗法，我地可以參考以前d演藝圈整個#向前線消防員致敬個hashtag，瘋狂係社交網站例如twitter ig sc etc整到變trending<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/geXPpvN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgeXPpvN.png&h=d9c1eeac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7twpdo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7twpdo8.png&h=3f7bdc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，我地每個人係紙寫低#向香港年輕人致敬，如下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhUY2ij.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhUY2ij.png&h=7175f0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，我地利用近排全世界好hit既老人filter，黎個反向crossover自拍po上社交網站，儘量令全世界人都見到我地支持香港年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三，連登巴絲瘋狂係社交網站炒起個話題，令全世界人都繼續關注hk發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n最後，睇到前排銀髮族遊行覺得好感動，我地係時候同老人家大和解了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n效果圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGdrrNE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGdrrNE.png&h=db7129bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b04b2af4cf6dd5dada5ea05aac35943550cb2a","tid":1329460,"uid":244521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"劉明一身蟻"},{"pid":"5ccf5b1e9c5d6dc684b92ff6ba29d318eb26dffc","tid":1329460,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"403aec74e7f881e4a9f448eb2043de6c0332eb54","tid":1329460,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:18:46.000Z","msg":"我要痾屎"},{"pid":"16118dc4b0b3ef7ec818d163a301ed4b290df24c","tid":1329460,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59b04b2af4cf6dd5dada5ea05aac35943550cb2a","tid":1329460,"uid":244521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"劉明一身蟻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62df57cbaa7ba06a009dd71ce85770f329c16019","tid":1329460,"uid":72420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"一係年輕人，一係青年人，冇年青人"},{"pid":"9d25b27b1287531d597455c630355637f5393663","tid":1329460,"uid":72420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62df57cbaa7ba06a009dd71ce85770f329c16019","tid":1329460,"uid":72420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"一係年輕人，一係青年人，冇年青人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"或者青少年"},{"pid":"a375ccffc539a6c09e8e6ddc242f98ce5feeadce","tid":1329460,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d25b27b1287531d597455c630355637f5393663","tid":1329460,"uid